{"tid":2082691,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屌！唔撚食KFC！自己整蘑菇飯！","createTime":"2020-06-28T08:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T19:43:43.000Z","uid":68594,"like":44,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e8e26f2435ead8adccb34c684cbbbcdb09137df9","tid":2082691,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T08:42:36.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係子言張！<br />\n<br />\n仆街真係好想食蘑菇飯！但係唔撚想食KFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我決定自己整！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_IcDBvpTZW0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_IcDBvpTZW0&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtBPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=3c6932c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_IcDBvpTZW0</a><br />\n<br />\n🔴材料<br />\n大啡菇....................4隻<br />\n蒜頭.........................2個<br />\n牛油.......................40克<br />\n麵粉......................40克<br />\n上湯.................250毫升<br />\n<br />\n🔴調味料<br />\n胡椒粉、蠔油、老抽、鹽、糖、雞粉<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n🔴步驟<br />\n1.大啡菇切片、菇蒂切碎<br />\n2.拍扁蒜頭，去皮切碎，倒進菇碎內<br />\n3.冷鑊落油，油熱後先炒香菇碎及蒜頭碎<br />\n4.略炒一分鐘後加入菇片，收乾大部分水份後上碟<br />\n5.融化一塊牛油，然後落麵粉<br />\n6.倒入一整盒高湯，煮至麵粉完全融化<br />\n7.倒入與高湯同等份量的清水<br />\n8.加入胡椒粉、鹽、糖、雞粉、老抽、蠔油<br />\n9.蘑菇汁開始變得濃稠，就可以倒入蘑菇，多煮兩至三分鐘<br />\n10.把蘑菇及蘑菇汁倒上白飯上"},{"pid":"4602d2554b25bcad4a1c3e5d7c8f66c005d3b444","tid":2082691,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T08:44:57.000Z","msg":"用真屎？"},{"pid":"4185bca6bda9f4aad74ac920a4ea6277f25a3850","tid":2082691,"uid":194326,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T08:45:49.000Z","msg":"煮過<br />\n煮完仲貴過直接買，仲要難食"},{"pid":"8c6144f7091fd316ebbfb7c8ffab237750fd98c5","tid":2082691,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T08:46:12.000Z","msg":"乜D掟唔係好濕嘅咩？可以食？"},{"pid":"e27948823b5f2aea912d5a92ba4c7eb145e16e7a","tid":2082691,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy"